description:
Proper Japanese Title: デスバザー日和! (Desu Bazā Biyori!)

Clay's investigation into the Traitors narrows down Shaula Gorgon as a likely suspect. The NOT class girls have a study session at Deathbucks. Later, the girls attend the Death Bazaar free market, where Eternal Feather's unlucky streak turns grim.
name: Nice Day for a Death Bazaar!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: つぐみスパイラル! (Tsugumi Supairaru!)

Dr. Stein is able to save Eternal Feather's life, and teases our heroines as she recovers. Tsugumi and Meme share some Japanese ways to keep cool in the summer. Tsugumi laments not being able to defend her meister, which is why she hasn’t chosen one.
name: Tsugumi Spiral!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: カボチャ,グローウィン! (Kabocha, Gurōwin!)

A collection of four short stories chronicles the passing of summer, as the girls grow pumpkins for Halloween. A hot night spells trouble sleeping. Meme has a short-term memory misadventure. Tsugumi teaches Anya about baseball. The girls each write home.
name: Pumpkin Growing!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 悪夢のはじまり! (Akumu no Hajimari!)

Tsugumi is devastated by news of her pet dog's death. She lashes out at Meme, who later that night sleepwalks to DWMA. Meme is suspected of being controlled by Shaula, and placed in DWMA custody. When Anya and Tsugumi visit, things soon get out of hand!
name: The Beginning of the Nightmare!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: それぞれの覚悟! (Sorezore no Kakugo!)

Anya, under escort by Clay and Akane, passes the Battle Festival grounds, where Shaula's followers attack! Tsugumi also flees house arrest to try to meet up with Anya, so together they can save Meme. Dr. Stein works on an antidote to Shaula's poison.
name: Their Various Resolves!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 魂の共鳴! (Tamashī no Kyōmei!)

With the antidote in hand, Tsugumi and Anya fight desperately to release Meme from Shaula's mind control. The fighting spreads throughout town, until it even reaches the girls' dorm. Tsugumi comes to a decision that will affect all three of their lives.
name: Soul Resonance!

description: Proper Japanese Title: ?
name: Personal Entertainment AI! Hackadoll!

description: Proper Japanese Title: ?
name: Please Let Us Be Idols!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 始まってるよ！これが野乃本魔法拳！ (Hajimatteru yo! Kore ga Nono hon Mahō ken!)

Somera-chan is magical. Somera-chan is poor. Somera-chan gets turned into a human wreath by a deceptively peaceful alpaca.
name: Here We Go! Say Hello to the Nonomoto Magic Fist

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ガリバーを縛る雑兵たち〜アラスカ極寒環境雪上戦Ⅰ 〜 (Garibā o shibaru zōhyō-tachi 〜 Arasuka gokkan kankyō setsujō-sen Ⅰ 〜)

The world is now fragmented into four coalitions that constantly wage wars across their many borders. These wars are fought by a new class of weapons called Objects, which rendered all other forms of conventional warfare obsolete.
name: The Little Soldiers Who Tie Down Gulliver / The Snowy Deep Winter Battle of Alaska I

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ?

Yuta Hoshitani, a first year at Ayanagi Academy, finds out about auditions for the musical department and applies with his new friend, Nayuki.
name: Act 1

description: Proper Japanese Title: 小森さんは頼まれますか？ (Komori-san wa Tanoma Remasu ka?)
name: A Request for Komori-san?

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 鉄と血と (Tetsu to Chi to)

Mikazuki belongs to the private security company CGS, at the Martian city of Chryse, which has been hired to escort a girl named Kudelia to Earth. But just as preparations for departure are underway, Gjallarhorn attacks CGS in an attempt on Kudelia's life.
name: Iron and Blood...

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 最強の男 (Saikyō no Otoko)

Saitama is a guy who’s a hero for fun. After saving a child from certain death, he decided to become a hero and trained hard for three years. Though he’s now so strong he can defeat any opponent with a single punch, lately he feels as if, in exchange for overwhelming power, he’s lost something even more important.
name: The Strongest Man

description: Proper Japanese Title: ハコネちゃん降臨！ (Hakone-chan kōrin!)
name: Hakone-chan Arrives!

description:
Proper Japanese Title: 入学！巨人中学校 (Nyūgaku! Kyojin Chūgakkō)

On the very first day of junior high, Eren oversleeps and is woken up by Mikasa. While rushing to school, he runs into several of his classmates. When they arrive at school, everyone except Eren notices something is odd.
name: Starting School! Titan Junior High School

description:
Proper Japanese Title: ようこそ庶民 (Yōkoso shomin)

Entirely average high school student Kimito Kagurazaka is snatched out of his regular school and sent to an elite all-girl school in order to acclimate the students there to both boys and to the culture of commoners.
name: Welcome, Commoner

series.name: Ore ga Ojōsama Gakkō ni "Shomin Sanpuru" Toshite Rachirareta Ken

description: Proper Japanese Title: ?
name: The Missing Bike Knows Part 1

description: Proper Japanese Title: ?
name: Where's the Doctor?

description: Cordelia has a vision in which Gunn is fighting for his life. With Angel spending larger amounts of time asleep due to Darla's influence, Cordelia can't wake him and ends up going to help Gunn by herself. Gunn and Cordelia then spend the episode together trying to find a demon, Deevak, from Cordelia's vision, and also search for Angel's stolen car. While engaged in this mission, the two learn a bit about each other and Gunn learns to see Cordelia as not just a "stick figure Barbie" who is useless. Cordelia impresses upon Gunn that he is taking unnecessary risks and putting himself too much in danger--the same problem his sister complained about before her death. Angel and Wesley arrive to help Gunn and Cordelia at the last moment, and then Angel goes home and surrenders himself to his dreams with Darla.
name: First Impressions

description: Rick and the group are still having trouble assimilating into Alexandria. Will a new threat bring them closer together or drive them further apart?
name: First Time Again

has_staff_review.name: The Walking Dead Episode 601: "First Time Again"

description: Predacons have come! The Autobots must defeat a gigantic hand!
name: Battle Protocol!

description: Miss Piggy gets jealous when she finds out the crew has party's without her after every show and Fozzie accidentally shoots Statler with a T-Shirt gun, hospitalizing him.
name: Pig Out

team_credits.name: Doctor Teeth and the Electric Mayhem

name: The One Where Pinkie Pie Knows

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: As things being to return to normal, a new problem arises for the Alexandrians.
name: JSS

description: Scotty Boom, a Chew Network super-chef, challenges Homer to a smoke-off.
name: Cue Detective

description: Upon learning that their father really died of lung cancer, Selma and Patty agree to quit smoking.
name: Puffless

description: When Lisa becomes scared at the Krustyland Halloween Horror Night, Homer is forced to take down his Everscream Terrors decorations. Halloween pop-up employees seek vengeance on Homer for causing them to lose their jobs, and rob his house while Homer and Lisa hide out in the attic. Homer and Lisa light up their stored holiday decorations to attract attention and stand up to the intruders.
name: Halloween of Horror

description: In the annual fright fest Halloween episode, Sideshow Bob finally kills Bart, only to reanimate him; Homer wakes up with short-term memory loss; and Lisa, Bart, and Milhouse get super powers from radiation.
name: Treehouse of Horror XXVI

description: When Groot is infected by a parasitic fungus, the Guardians must embark on a perilous journey in order to save him.
name: Can't Fight This Seedling

description: Galavan and Penguin join forces with a dangerous family in Gotham. Then, as the rivalry between the Waynes and the Galavans resurfaces, Gordon struggles to maintain order in the city.
name: Scarification

description: Ahsoka sends the Rebel crew to find and recruit a war hero to their cause, but when they discover it is Captain Rex, trust issues put the mission at risk.
name: The Lost Commanders

description: When Barry (Grant Gustin) and the team find out Captain Cold (guest-star Wentworth Miller) has been kidnapped, they form an uneasy alliance with his sister, Lisa (guest-star Peyton List). However, Barry feels double-crossed when he finds out Snart is working with his father, Lewis Snart (guest-star Michael Ironside) on a heist. Meanwhile, Joe (Jesse L. Martin) is faced with a difficult decision.
name: Family of Rogues

description: The growing tension between Oliver (Stephen Amell) and Diggle (David Ramsey) puts both their lives at risk when they go after Damien Darhk (guest star Neal McDonough) and a H.I.V.E. deployed meta-human. Meanwhile, Laurel (Katie Cassidy) talks Thea (Willa Holland) into returning to Nanda Parbat to ask her father (John Barrowman) to put Sara (guest star Caity Lotz) into the Lazarus Pit. However, Laurel is surprised when Nyssa (guest star Katrina Law) refuses to do it.
name: Restoration

description:
Noah Bennet (Jack Coleman) takes matters into his own hands to get much-needed answers. After Tommy (Robbie Kay) makes a startling discovery, he and Emily (Gatlin Green) go on an unexpected journey. Elsewhere, Luke (Zachary Levi) continues to come to grips with the fact that he has become what he has been hunting. Malina (Danika Yarosh) finds a surprising ally. Miko (Kiki Sukezane) stays on the course to save her father, but Erica (Rya Khilstedt) takes measures to interfere.

Meanwhile, Carlos (Ryan Guzman) learns more about what is really going on with EVOS from an unlikely source.
name: Game Over

description: Amethyst and Steven get in on some Gem gossip.
name: Too Far

description: After her dramatic rescue from another planet, Simmons is still reeling from her ordeal and reveals how she had to fight for her life in a harsh new world.
name: 4,722 Hours

description: Proper Japanese Title: 続けようぜビルス様！神と神の戦いを！ (Tsudukeyō ze Birusu-sama! Kami to Kami no Tatakai o!)
name: Let's Keep Going Lord Beerus! The Battle of Gods Continues!

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Proper Japanese Title: 宇宙が砕ける！？激突！破壊神ＶＳ超サイヤ人ゴッド！(Uchū ga Kudakeru! Haikaishin Tai Sūpā Saiya-jin Goddo!)
name: The Universe Crumbles?! Clash! The God of Destruction vs. Super Saiyan God!

description: Proper Japanese Title: 悟空よ、超サイヤ人ゴッドを越えて行け！(Gokū yo, Sūpā Saiya-jin Goddo o Koete Ike!)
name: Goku, Go Surpass Super Saiyan God!

description: Proper Japanese Title: これがオラのありったけの力だ！決着！神と神 (Kore ga Ora no Arittake no Chikarada! Ketchaku! Kami to Kami)
name: This is Every Last Bit of My Power! The Battle of Gods Concludes!

description: Proper Japanese Title: 勇者サタンよ奇跡を起こせ！宇宙からの挑戦状！！(Yūsha Satan yo Kiseki o Okose! Uchū Kara no Chōsenjō!!)
name: Heroic Satan, Cause a Miracle! A Challenge From Outer Space!!

description: Proper Japanese Title: ベジータが弟子入り！？ウイスを攻略せよ！(Bejīta ga Deshi’iri!? Uisu o Kōryakuse yo!)
name: Vegeta Becomes a Pupil?! Take Down Whis!

description: Rick and his group get caught up in a dangerous little town on the road back to Alexandria. Meanwhile, Daryl, Sasha and Abraham continue to lead away the remaining walkers away from the safe-zone.
name: Thank You

description: Twenty-four-year-old Kara Zor-El, cousin of Superman, who was taken in by the Danvers family when she was 12 after being sent away from Krypton, must learn to embrace her powers after previously hiding them.
name: Pilot

description: After Bridgit Pike (guest star Michelle Veintimilla) rejoins her brothers, a new spark of courage ignites within her, as she chooses to take control of her future. Meanwhile, Kringle and Nygma's relationship will take a new step and Penguin and Galavan continue to battle for control of Gotham City's underworld.
name: By Fire

has_staff_review.name: The Flash Episode 204: "The Fury of Firestorm"

description: The stakes get even higher as Hunter and May continue to go after Ward and HYDRA, and Daisy and Coulson begin to suspect that the ATCU may be keeping a big secret from S.H.I.E.L.D.
name: Among Us Hide...

has_staff_review.name: Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. Episode #306 - "Among Us Hide..."

description: Miss Piggy's feud with Reese Witherspoon over a role in the movie Walk the Line becomes extreme. Meanwhile Fozzie starts making actually funny jokes... on his girlfriends expense and Rizzo crashes into Scooter's car damaging it.
name: Swine Walk

first_appearance_teams.name: Doctor Teeth and the Electric Mayhem

team_credits.name: Doctor Teeth and the Electric Mayhem

description: The Team meets a strange alien robot called the Fugitoid.
name: Beyond The Known Universe

deck: Ash and Pablo go on the road to fight the Evil Dead.
description: Special Agent Fisher is tracking Ash. Pablo gets his first taste of blood in a manic showdown, and a revelation changes Kelly's life forever.
name: Bait

deck: Supergirl realizes being a hero isn't as easy as she thought.
description: When Kara’s attempts to help National City don’t go according to plan, she must put aside the doubts that she – and the city’s media – has about her abilities in order to capture an escapee from the Kryptonian prison, Fort Rozz. Also, Cat pressures James to use his connection to Superman to get her an interview with Supergirl.
name: Stronger Together

description: Team Arrow discover that a gang of crooked cops is robbing drug dealers and selling their product. Oliver turns to Quentin for help, but soon learns that he is working with Damian. Meanwhile, Laurel brings Sara to Star City and reunites her with Quentin, but his reaction isn't what she had hoped.
name: Beyond Redemption
Where There's A Will, There's A Wraith

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Robin refuses to give the Titans any more orders so that they'll learn to think for themselves. Instead, the Titans start taking their cues from fortune cookies.
name: Accept the Next Proposition You Hear

description: Control Freak informs the Titans that they are on a TV show he created and demands they earn him an award.
name: The Fourth Wall

description: Cyborg's real strength comes not from his robot parts, but from his favorite song.
Robin tries to teach the Titans valuable life lessons by reading them fairytales, but the others co-opt his stories and spin them into their own twisted yarns.
name: Grube's Fairytales

description: Brother Blood takes the Titans to trial for their recent destruction of Jump City.
name: A Farce

description: The Titans' Halloween party is interrupted by the Hive Five robbing a candy factory.
name: Scary Figure Dance

description: Caught red-handed by Titus, the Guardians are coerced into infiltrating a notorious gang of weapons dealers known as the Black Order.
name: Undercover Angle

description: Butch leads Penguin and his men to the warehouse where Gertrude is being held, as Penguin plots his revenge on Galavan for kidnapping his mother. Meanwhile, Nygma deals with the aftermath of a deadly accident.
name: Mommy's Little Monster

description: Supergirl's powers are tested when Reactron, one of Superman's formidable enemies, arrives in National City and targets the young hero. Also, Cat plans to run an expose on Supergirl.
name: Fight or Flight

description:
In an effort to get answers, Noah Bennet (Jack Coleman) joins forces with Hiro Nakamura (guest-star Masi Oka) to return to the day of the tragic events of June 13, 2014 that set everything in motion. On the verge of delivering a speech to commemorate the event, Mohinder Suresh (guest-star Sendhill Ramamurthy) receives a dire message from Angela Petrelli (guest-star Cristine Rose) about Erica Kravid's (Rya Khilstedt) true motives. In Japan, Hachiro Otomo (guest-star Hiro Kanagawa) makes a calculated move against Hiro Nakamura.

Meanwhile, a much happier Luke (Zachary Levi) and Joanne (Judi Shekoni) come to Odessa in hopes of finding a cure to their son's ailment.
name: June 13th Part One

description: Ezra and the crew begin to develop friendships with Captain Rex and his colleagues.
name: Relics of The Old Republic

description: Ezra, Sabine, Zeb and Chopper venture on a mission to an abandoned medical station in search of supplies for the fleet. When the arrival of two Inquisitors sent by Darth Vader puts Sabine and Ezra in peril, Zeb and Chopper devise a plan to save their friends.
name: Always Two There Are

description: The survivors must ask themselves who can be trusted, and better yet, can they change?
name: Here's Not Here

has_staff_review.name: The Walking Dead Episode 604: "Here's Not Here"

description: For Regular Show's fifth installment of 'Terror Tales,' Benson tries to spice up the park's annual Halloween party; by renting a wish-making machine.
name: Terror Tales of The Park V

description: When things take a turn for the worse with Sara (guest-star Caity Lotz), Oliver (Stephen Amell) calls in a favor from an old friend who deals in the mystical, John Constantine (guest star Matt Ryan).
name: Haunted

description: Barry (Grant Gustin) learns a new breacher, Dr. Light, has come through the portal and sets off to capture her. Jay (guest-star Teddy Sears) tells Barry that Dr. Light was not a threat on Earth-2 and that Barry can reason with her. However, during a fight with The Flash, she blinds him and drops some shocking news about Zoom. Meanwhile, Barry and Patty (Shantel VanSanten) go out on a date.
name: The Darkness and the Light

has_staff_review.name: The Flash Episode 205 - "The Darkness and the Light"

description: Galavan sends Barbara after Jim Gordon, while he tries to make a business deal with Bruce Wayne. Barnes and Bullock are hot on Barbara's trail, and Nygma has a run-in with a familiar face.
name: Tonight's the Night

deck: When the team crash lands on an ice moon along with the enemy, they must put their differences aside to survive.
name: The Moons of Thalos 3

description: As Agent Daisy Johnson and the team fight to protect Inhumans, S.H.I.E.L.D. discovers the shocking truth about one of their biggest foes. Meanwhile, Agent Leo Fitz helps Agent Jemma Simmons recover information that could lead them back through the portal.
name: Chaos Theory

series.name: My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic

description: Proper Japanese Title: パン誕生！そして悟空は修行の旅へ！？(Pan Tanjō! Soshite Gokū wa Shugyō no Tabi e!?)
name: Pan is Born! And Goku Goes Off on a Training Journey?!

description: Liv (Rose McIver) unwittingly crosses paths with the most dangerous man in Seattle while investigating the murder of degenerate gambler Harry (guest-star Ray Galletti). Detective Babineaux (Malcolm Goodwin) has a super-fan moment when he and Liv question NBA Hall of Famer Calvin Owens (guest-star Rick Fox) at Harry's funeral. Meanwhile, Blaine's (David Anders) father (guest-star Robert Knepper ) makes a huge discovery, and Ravi (Rahul Kohli) delivers some bad news. Major (Robert Buckley) continues to struggle.
name: Max Wager

description: In the wake of an unspeakable tragedy, Erica Kravid (Rya Khilstedt) puts her dark plan into motion with Renautas. Hiro (guest-star Masi Oka) and Angela (guest-star Cristine Rose) are tasked with an important mission that could change the course of humanity. In Odessa, a distraught Luke (Zachary Levi) and Joanne (Judi Shekoni) come to realize their tragic mission after the loss of their son. Meanwhile, Noah Bennet (Jack Coleman) has an unexpected reunion with Matt Parkman (guest star Greg Grunberg). In Japan, the origins of Miko (Kiki Sukezane) come to light. Elsewhere, the truth behind Carlos' (Ryan Guzman) military service is revealed.
name: June 13th Part Two

description: Trouble is inside and outside the gate.
name: Now

description: Gordon and Barnes continue cleaning up Gotham, and Gordon comes face-to-face with one of the city's most dangerous hitmen, Eduardo Flamingo (guest-star Raul Castillo). Meanwhile, Nygma and Penguin cross paths again, and Bruce pressures Galavan into handing over the name of his parents' murderer.
name: A Bitter Pill to Swallow

description: Kara's two identities are stretched thin when Supergirl must protect National City from a series of bombings and Kara is tasked with babysitting Cat's son, Carter. Also, James is conflicted when his ex-girlfriend Lucy Lane seeks to rekindle their relationship.
name: How Does She Do It?
